HEADWORD: claxon
<hw>claxon</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a kind of loud horn formerly used on
motor vehicles.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> klaxon.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

