==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: claxon
<hw>claxon</hw> <pos>v.</pos> <def>to sound loudly; -- of car
horns.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> honk, blare, beep, toot, klaxon.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>to use the horn of a car.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> honk.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

